QuoteText: well, if you are right then think about it : they considered millions of people inferior so they made the choice for them I imagine. so the Nazis were pro-choice
ResponseText: I'm still confused by this comment. Did you actually mean that? If you did, that is not Pro-choice but Pro-abortion. Women did not have a choice in whether their pregnancies were terminated or not which, having it, is the definition of the PC point of view. So no, they were NOT Pro-choice.
